Geometric diagram and optical property of GaN nano-fin. (a) Geometric diagram of a GaN nano-fin on a silica substrate, where d1 is the thickness of the nano-fin. (b) Transmittance, PCE, and overall PCE versus the thickness of the nano-fin under light illumination of 633 nm at normal incidence along the z-direction from bottom to up. The polarized light is along the x-direction. The light is x-polarized, with λ = 633 nm. The light impinges perpendicularly onto the structure from bottom along the positive z-direction.

